text: Mohamad Kasem (; born 3 October 1993) is a Syrian judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's 73 kg, where he was eliminated by An Chang-rim in the second round. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Syrian male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Syria Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Judoka at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Kurash practitioners at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Syria
